snippet.title: Door Kickers: Action Squad Release Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/686200/Door_Kickers_Action_Squad/

Rescue hostages, disarm bombs and save the day in this old school, side-scroller action game with retro graphics and retro sensibilities. Online and Couch Coop Included.
